data.description: This is a rarity! This sprawling 4 bedroom ranch home that is located in  a well sought after area is available now!. As you walk into the front door you are looking at a very spacious living room that has new carpet & hardwood floors with a 2 sided fireplace from the living room to the kitchen area which has beautiful Bertch cabinetry & Nichols Home Improvements countertops. Wait, there is more....you also have a spacious family room in the lower level. Also this home offers a good size 2 stall attached garage and a 3/4 of an acre well landscape lot. You will find your family will be excited to celebrate the holidays in your new home. Schedule your showings today, this is a must see.
